title: DEATHGAZE - Complete Discography
description:
This is the complete discography of the Japanese metal band, DEATHGAZE.  This torrent has every maxi-single the band has released, the full-length album, the latest single "abyss", and the live mini-album "genocidal freaks death code=[2F0U0C6K1E2R110]" featuring the unreleased track "scatologist".  If you&#039;d like any other similar-sounding Japanese metal, feel free to ask me, and I&#039;ll upload more.

Check out my journal entry on Last.fm--http://www.last.fm/user/GrannyGreen/journal/2008/01/20/7hc0b_my_cd_collection--for an up-to-date list on all the CDs that I own.  Feel free to ask for a rip of any one there...I&#039;ll rip it in any quality you want.
